      "representation": "view",
      "value": "<div class=\"contentLayout2\"><style>[data-colorid=hfz0xy2q9e]{color:#4c9aff} html[data-color-mode=dark] [data-colorid=hfz0xy2q9e]{color:#004eb3}[data-colorid=s83m9ao0nu]{color:#4c9aff} html[data-color-mode=dark] [data-colorid=s83m9ao0nu]{color:#004eb3}[data-colorid=mamv8lceel]{color:#4c9aff} html[data-color-mode=dark] [data-colorid=mamv8lceel]{color:#004eb3}[data-colorid=fy0ljwrb0z]{color:#4c9aff} html[data-color-mode=dark] [data-colorid=fy0ljwrb0z]{color:#004eb3}[data-colorid=cp6ulz778c]{color:#4c9aff} html[data-color-mode=dark] [data-colorid=cp6ulz778c]{color:#004eb3}[data-colorid=cliwzpiy1i]{color:#4c9aff} html[data-color-mode=dark] [data-colorid=cliwzpiy1i]{color:#004eb3}[data-colorid=vj6u7btuty]{color:#4c9aff} html[data-color-mode=dark] [data-colorid=vj6u7btuty]{color:#004eb3}[data-colorid=nl1e6dq0ma]{color:#4c9aff} html[data-color-mode=dark] [data-colorid=nl1e6dq0ma]{color:#004eb3}</style>\n<div class=\"columnLayout fixed-width\" data-layout=\"fixed-width\">\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" alt=\"sorindar-banner.jpg\" width=\"760\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/604635137/sorindar-banner.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1758110676465&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=760&amp;height=214\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/604635137/sorindar-banner.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1758110676465&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"541\" data-width=\"1920\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"603979929\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"sorindar-banner.jpg\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/jpeg\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"604635137\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"5\" data-media-id=\"18868d42-2e79-4726-90a7-dcbe7e0870f5\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/604635137/sorindar-banner.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1758110676465&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=1520&amp;height=428 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/604635137/sorindar-banner.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1758110676465&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=760&amp;height=214 1x\" /></span></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"columnLayout three-equal\" data-layout=\"three-equal\">\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<p><strong><span data-colorid=\"cp6ulz778c\">Project</span></strong>: Creating Sorindar, the Gray Rock Dragon</p><p><strong><span data-colorid=\"nl1e6dq0ma\">Created &amp; Written by</span></strong>: Johnny Fehr</p><p><strong><span data-colorid=\"mamv8lceel\">Edited by:</span></strong> Leif Pedersen</p></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<p /></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<a class=\"external-link\" href=\"https://downloads.renderman.pixar.com/Tutorials/sorindar/sorindar-dragon-RfH.zip\" rel=\"nofollow\"><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-right-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-right\" alt=\"DownloadButton2.png\" width=\"158\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/604635137/DownloadButton2.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1758108719241&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=158&amp;height=37\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/604635137/DownloadButton2.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1758108719241&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"68\" data-width=\"286\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"604635270\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"DownloadButton2.png\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/png\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"604635137\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"5\" data-media-id=\"5a6faeb6-d136-407b-87c8-8c953a610f30\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/604635137/DownloadButton2.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1758108719241&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=286&amp;height=68 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/604635137/DownloadButton2.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1758108719241&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=158&amp;height=37 1x\" /></span></a><p /></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"columnLayout fixed-width\" data-layout=\"fixed-width\">\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<p>After finding <a class=\"external-link\" href=\"https://www.artstation.com/kamiga\" rel=\"nofollow\">Cl&eacute;ment B&eacute;ziers'</a> wonderful work, I decided to reach out to take his model for a personal creative spin in Mari and RenderMan for Houdini &hellip; and the 3D community never disappoints &hellip; as Cl&eacute;ment B&eacute;ziers didn't hesitate for a second to get excited about the creative collaboration!</p><p>Let's break down some of the key look development processes with Mari and Industrial Light &amp; Magic's awesome material layering system, MaterialX Lama.</p><hr /></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"columnLayout two-right-sidebar\" data-layout=\"two-right-sidebar\">\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<a href=\"/wiki/spaces/RU/pages/657555575/Dragon+Modeling\" data-linked-resource-id=\"657555575\" data-linked-resource-version=\"2\" data-linked-resource-type=\"page\"><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" alt=\"dragon_modelling_thumb.jpg\" width=\"586\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/604635137/dragon_modelling_thumb.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1762591968998&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=586&amp;height=255\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/604635137/dragon_modelling_thumb.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1762591968998&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"255\" data-width=\"586\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"657621235\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"dragon_modelling_thumb.jpg\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/jpeg\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"604635137\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"5\" data-media-id=\"e07d8981-a49b-4809-b6a5-41ad6824ddcd\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/604635137/dragon_modelling_thumb.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1762591968998&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=586&amp;height=255 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/604635137/dragon_modelling_thumb.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1762591968998&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=586&amp;height=255 1x\" /></span></a></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"cell aside\" data-type=\"aside\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<h1 id=\"Sorindar,theGrayRockDragon-Modeling\"><span data-colorid=\"s83m9ao0nu\">Modeling</span></h1><p /></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"columnLayout two-right-sidebar\" data-layout=\"two-right-sidebar\">\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<a href=\"/wiki/spaces/RU/pages/657621209/Dragon+Texturing\" data-linked-resource-id=\"657621209\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"page\"><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" alt=\"dragon_texturing_thumb.jpg\" width=\"586\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/604635137/dragon_texturing_thumb.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1762592087989&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=586&amp;height=255\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/604635137/dragon_texturing_thumb.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1762592087989&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"255\" data-width=\"586\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"656998785\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"dragon_texturing_thumb.jpg\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/jpeg\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"604635137\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"5\" data-media-id=\"d48c3adc-9233-4559-af2b-ea5607f72b89\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/604635137/dragon_texturing_thumb.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1762592087989&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=586&amp;height=255 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/604635137/dragon_texturing_thumb.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1762592087989&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=586&amp;height=255 1x\" /></span></a></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"cell aside\" data-type=\"aside\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<h1 id=\"Sorindar,theGrayRockDragon-Texturing\"><span data-colorid=\"vj6u7btuty\">Texturing</span></h1><p /></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"columnLayout two-right-sidebar\" data-layout=\"two-right-sidebar\">\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<a href=\"/wiki/spaces/RU/pages/656834669/Dragon+Lighting\" data-linked-resource-id=\"656834669\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"page\"><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" alt=\"dragon_lighting_thumb.jpg\" width=\"586\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/604635137/dragon_lighting_thumb.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1762592147987&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=586&amp;height=255\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/604635137/dragon_lighting_thumb.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1762592147987&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"255\" data-width=\"586\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"657260663\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"dragon_lighting_thumb.jpg\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/jpeg\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"604635137\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"5\" data-media-id=\"7925b108-ceff-4978-aaff-0a988d7b3e10\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/604635137/dragon_lighting_thumb.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1762592147987&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=586&amp;height=255 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/604635137/dragon_lighting_thumb.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1762592147987&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=586&amp;height=255 1x\" /></span></a></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"cell aside\" data-type=\"aside\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<h1 id=\"Sorindar,theGrayRockDragon-Lighting\"><span data-colorid=\"fy0ljwrb0z\">Lighting</span></h1><p /></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"columnLayout two-right-sidebar\" data-layout=\"two-right-sidebar\">\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<a href=\"/wiki/spaces/RU/pages/657162354/Dragon+Rendering\" data-linked-resource-id=\"657162354\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"page\"><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" alt=\"dragon_rendering_thumb.jpg\" width=\"586\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/604635137/dragon_rendering_thumb.jpg?version=2&amp;modificationDate=1762592272053&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=586&amp;height=255\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/604635137/dragon_rendering_thumb.jpg?version=2&amp;modificationDate=1762592272053&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"255\" data-width=\"586\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"657260672\" data-linked-resource-version=\"2\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"dragon_rendering_thumb.jpg\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/jpeg\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"604635137\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"5\" data-media-id=\"043fad44-8e50-45b7-8745-8c996a48a534\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/604635137/dragon_rendering_thumb.jpg?version=2&amp;modificationDate=1762592272053&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=586&amp;height=255 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/604635137/dragon_rendering_thumb.jpg?version=2&amp;modificationDate=1762592272053&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=586&amp;height=255 1x\" /></span></a></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"cell aside\" data-type=\"aside\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<h1 id=\"Sorindar,theGrayRockDragon-Rendering\"><span data-colorid=\"hfz0xy2q9e\">Rendering</span></h1><p /></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"columnLayout two-right-sidebar\" data-layout=\"two-right-sidebar\">\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<a href=\"/wiki/spaces/RU/pages/657621227/Dragon+Compositing\" data-linked-resource-id=\"657621227\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"page\"><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" alt=\"dragon_rendering_thumb.jpg\" width=\"586\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/604635137/dragon_rendering_thumb.jpg?version=2&amp;modificationDate=1762592272053&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=586&amp;height=255\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/604635137/dragon_rendering_thumb.jpg?version=2&amp;modificationDate=1762592272053&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"255\" data-width=\"586\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"657260672\" data-linked-resource-version=\"2\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"dragon_rendering_thumb.jpg\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/jpeg\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"604635137\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"5\" data-media-id=\"043fad44-8e50-45b7-8745-8c996a48a534\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/604635137/dragon_rendering_thumb.jpg?version=2&amp;modificationDate=1762592272053&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=586&amp;height=255 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/604635137/dragon_rendering_thumb.jpg?version=2&amp;modificationDate=1762592272053&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=586&amp;height=255 1x\" /></span></a><p /></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"cell aside\" data-type=\"aside\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<h1 id=\"Sorindar,theGrayRockDragon-Compositing\"><span data-colorid=\"cliwzpiy1i\">Compositing</span></h1><p /></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"columnLayout fixed-width\" data-layout=\"fixed-width\">\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<hr /><h3 style=\"text-align: center;\" id=\"Sorindar,theGrayRockDragon-AbouttheArtists\">About the Artists</h3></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"columnLayout two-equal\" data-layout=\"two-equal\">\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<a class=\"external-link\" href=\"https://www.artstation.com/johnnyfehr\" rel=\"nofollow\"><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" alt=\"johnny-fehr-headshot.jpg\" width=\"202\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/604635137/johnny-fehr-headshot.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1758109361838&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=202&amp;height=202\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/604635137/johnny-fehr-headshot.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1758109361838&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"1024\" data-width=\"1024\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"604143718\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"johnny-fehr-headshot.jpg\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/jpeg\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"604635137\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"5\" data-media-id=\"56c830ba-2572-41dd-8213-2e45d4ff9839\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/604635137/johnny-fehr-headshot.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1758109361838&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=404&amp;height=404 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/604635137/johnny-fehr-headshot.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1758109361838&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=202&amp;height=202 1x\" /></span></a><p>Johnny Fehr works at DNEG in Vancouver as a texturing and look-dev artist.  He also works as a teacher and mentor at PIXL VISN in Germany and VIA University College in Denmark<br />&rdquo;For me, surfacing is a way of storytelling and brings grey models to life&rdquo;</p></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<a class=\"external-link\" href=\"https://www.artstation.com/kamiga\" rel=\"nofollow\"><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" alt=\"clement-beziers-headshot.jpg\" width=\"200\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/604635137/clement-beziers-headshot.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1758109384545&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=200&amp;height=200\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/604635137/clement-beziers-headshot.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1758109384545&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"1024\" data-width=\"1024\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"604242120\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"clement-beziers-headshot.jpg\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/jpeg\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"604635137\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"5\" data-media-id=\"6a074548-1590-4426-bf5c-f970186e29e7\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/604635137/clement-beziers-headshot.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1758109384545&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=400&amp;height=400 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/604635137/clement-beziers-headshot.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1758109384545&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=200&amp;height=200 1x\" /></span></a><p>I am a self-taught artist with a passion for 3D art and specifically for the creation of imaginary yet realistic characters and creatures.</p><p /></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"columnLayout fixed-width\" data-layout=\"fixed-width\">\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<hr /><p>This project is available with an Attribution-NonCommercial 4.0 International License. This allows you to share and redistribute for non-commercial purposes, provided that you credit the original author.</p><div class=\"confluence-information-macro confluence-information-macro-information conf-macro output-block\" data-hasbody=\"true\" data-macro-id=\"b2676109-51f7-43b2-b4c8-8d760e0c8979\" data-macro-name=\"info\"><span class=\"aui-icon aui-icon-small aui-iconfont-info confluence-information-macro-icon\"> </span><div class=\"confluence-information-macro-body\"><h3 id=\"Sorindar,theGrayRockDragon-Attribution-NonCommercial4.0International(CCBY-NC4.0)\">Attribution-NonCommercial 4.0 International (CC BY-NC 4.0)</h3></div></div><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" alt=\"by-nc.png\" width=\"97\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/604635137/by-nc.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1758108719456&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=97&amp;height=33\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki